#### BOSH Director
Ops Manager v1.11.0 uses BOSH v262, which includes the following changes to the BOSH Director:

+ Operators can now configure the number of workers that are available on the Bosh Director.
+ The Director Configuration form in OpsManager now includes a new field called “JMX Provider IP Address” that configures the JMX JSON plugin for secure transportation of metrics. 
+ Operators can use OpsManager API endpoints to view credentials that are stored in CredHub. For more information on how to do this visit [Fetching Variable Names and Values
](../credhub/credhub-api-variables.html).

